
Kconfig的作用是用来配置内核，它就是各种配置界面的源文件
AmbaConfig

------------

menu: 不可编辑的menu，
menuconfig: 带选项的menu

menu和choice的区别:
menu: 可以多选 
choice: 单项选择

//see linux/Documentation/kbuild/kconfig-languages.txt
------------------------------------------------------
mainmenu:

	"mainmenu" <prompt>

This sets the config program's title bar if the config program chooses
to use it. It should be placed at the top of the configuration, before any
other statement.
